query:
SELECT p.*, s.code as service_code, s.name as service_name, c.name as country_name 
FROM prices p 
JOIN services s ON p.serviceId = s.id 
JOIN countries c ON p.countryId = c.id 
WHERE s.code = 'test_api' 
LIMIT 1
